Interface GraphPanelListener


  • public interface GraphPanelListener
    Exposes a method that listens for click events on a GraphPanel object.

    • Method Detail

      • graphPanelClicked

        void graphPanelClicked(double timeStamp)
        This method is invoked when a GraphPanel object is clicked. The coordinates of the click on the graph plot are used to set a new selected time for the graph.
        Parameters:
        timeStamp - - The coordinatespoint on the graph plot where the mouse was clicked.
